"(define (hash-ref-ref hash . keys)
  (for/fold ([acc hash])
      ([key keys])
    (hash-ref acc key)))

(define (hash-ref-ref-noerr hash . keys)
  "On error, return #f."
  (for/fold ([acc hash])
      ([key keys])
    (if (and acc (hash-has-key? acc key))
        (hash-ref acc key)
        #f)))"
